-- Regression test: nested cons patterns at sibling positions. Under the old
-- constructor-only keying of the pattern-variable recycling map, the inner
-- `FOLLOWED BY` occurrences all reused one variable pair, producing
-- self-referential match constraints; with an OTHERWISE arm this shape
-- produced a bogus blocking redundancy warning, and without one it sent the
-- missing-branch expansion into an infinite loop (hanging `l4 check` and the
-- IDE). Must typecheck clean and evaluate.
GIVEN xs IS A LIST OF LIST OF MAYBE OF NUMBER
GIVETH A NUMBER
f xs MEANS
  CONSIDER xs
  WHEN ((JUST v) FOLLOWED BY b) FOLLOWED BY ((NOTHING FOLLOWED BY d) FOLLOWED BY rest) THEN 1
  OTHERWISE 0

#EVAL f (LIST (LIST (JUST 1)), (LIST NOTHING, JUST 2))
#EVAL f (LIST EMPTY)
